nitial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Independence Day: O Ressurgimento</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Esquadrão Suicida</span></em></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>', 1, 2, '2017-01-24 01:07:41', 71, 'Findreans ( Eduardo Castelhano )', '2017-03-03 21:35:04', 71, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-01-23 22:57:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '', 2, 6, 'Framboesa de Ouro, Razzies, Awards, premiação', 'Indicados do Framboesa de Ouro de 2017.', '', 1, 387);
INSERT INTO `Articles` (Id, Title, Alias, IntroText, FullText, State, Catid, CreatedDt, CreatedBy, CreatedByAlias, ModifiedDt, ModifiedBy, CheckedOut, CheckedOutTime, PublishUpDt, PublishDownDt, ImageIcon, Urls, Version, Ordering, Metadata, Metakey, MetaDesc, Access, Hits) VALUES
(2062, 'E agora os indicados do Oscar', 'e-agora-os-indicados-do-oscar', '<p>Depois das premiações de início do ano que antecedem essa, agora saiu a lista dos indicados ao Oscar desse ano.<img src="images/stories/oscar.jpg" alt="premiação do oscar" width="69" height="92" style="float: right; margin: 4px;" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Bem, nem posso dizer que tenha alguma surpresa, me parece mais estranho é que A Chegada tenha sido indicado a melhor filme. Eu diria que tem potencial, mas tudo me diz que La La Land deve ficar nas cabeças neste ano...</p>\r\n<p>Segue a listagem dos indicados abaixo, como sempre, filmes que não receberam nome em português ficaram com os títulos originais.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h3 style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1rem; font-size: 1.562rem; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; max-width: 636px;"><span style="font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; color: black;">Melhor Filme</span></h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">La La Land</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Moonlight</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Manchester à Beira-Mar</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">A Chegada</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Lion</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Até o Ultimo Homem</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Estrelas Além do Tempo</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Fences</span></em></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><em><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">A Qualquer Custo</span></em></p>\r\n<h3 style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1rem; font-size: 1.562rem; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; max-width: 636px;"><span style="font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; color: black;">Melhor Direção</span></h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Denis Villeneuve (<em>A Chegada</em>)</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Mel Gibson (<em>Até o Ultimo Homem</em>)</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Damien Chazelle (<em>La La Land</em>)</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Kenneth Lonergan (<em>Manchester à Beira-Mar</em>)</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Barry Jenkins (<em>Moonlight</em>)</span></p>\r\n<h3 style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1rem; font-size: 1.562rem; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; max-width: 636px;"><span style="font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; color: black;">Melhor Atriz</span></h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Emma Stone, <em>La La Land</em></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Natalie Portman, <em>Jackie</em></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Meryl Streep, <em>Florence - Quem é Essa Mulher?</em></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Isabelle Huppert, <em>Elle</em></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Georgia'',''serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #222222; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;">Ruth Negga, <em>Loving</em></span></p>\r\n<h3 style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1rem; font-size: 1.562rem; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; max-width: 636px;"><span style="font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; color: black;">Melhor Atriz Coadjuvante</span></h3>\r\n<p style="line-height: 21.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-orig